Stations <- read.csv("https://mcsp.wartburg.edu/letsche/cs205/DC-Stations.csv")

data_site <- "https://mcsp.wartburg.edu/letsche/cs205/2019-Q4-Trips-History-Data.rds"

Trips <- readRDS(gzcon(url(data_site)))

Trips %>% ggplot(aes(x=sdate))+
geom_density(fill= 'gray' , color = NA)

HowLong <- Trips %>% mutate(duration = as.numeric(edate- sdate)) %>% filter(duration < 60)

HowLong %>% ggplot(aes(y = duration , x = client)) + geom_boxplot(aes(color = client , fill = client)) + aes(alpha = .5, outlier.size = 2)

Hour of the day

Trips %>% mutate(H = lubridate::hour(sdate)) %>% ggplot(aes(x=H)) + geom_density(fill = "gray", adjust = 2) 

Trips %>% mutate(H = lubridate:: hour(sdate)) %>% group_by(H) %>% summarise(count = n()) %>% ggplot(aes(x= H, y= count))+ geom_point() + geom_line()

Day of the year

Trips %>% mutate(YD = lubridate:: yday(sdate)) %>% group_by(YD) %>% summarise(count = n()) %>% ggplot(aes(x= YD, y= count))+ geom_point() + geom_line()

## By client type

Trips %>% mutate(YD = lubridate:: yday(sdate)) %>% group_by(YD, client) %>% summarise(count = n()) %>% ggplot(aes(x= YD, y= count))+ geom_point() + geom_line() + facet_grid(client ~ .)

## Density

Trips %>% mutate(YD = lubridate::yday(sdate)) %>% ggplot(aes(x=YD)) + geom_density(fill = "gray", adjust = 2)

##Density By client Type

Trips %>% mutate(YD = lubridate::yday(sdate))%>% group_by(YD, client) %>% ggplot(aes(x=YD)) + geom_density(fill = "gray", adjust = 2) + facet_grid(client ~ .)

Day of the week

Trips %>% mutate(DW = lubridate:: wday(sdate)) %>% group_by(DW) %>% summarise(count = n()) %>% ggplot(aes(x= DW, y= count))+ geom_point() + geom_line()

## By client Type
Trips %>% mutate(DW = lubridate:: wday(sdate)) %>% group_by(DW , client) %>% summarise(count = n()) %>% ggplot(aes(x= DW, y= count))+ geom_point() + geom_line() + facet_grid(~client)

## density
Trips %>% mutate(WD = lubridate::wday(sdate))%>% group_by(WD, client) %>% ggplot(aes(x=WD)) + geom_density(fill = "gray", adjust = 2)

## Density by client Type
Trips %>% mutate(WD = lubridate::wday(sdate))%>% group_by(WD, client) %>% ggplot(aes(x=WD)) + geom_density(fill = "gray", adjust = 2) + facet_grid(client ~ .)

#How Far?

source("http://tiny.cc/dcf/haversine.R")
Simple <- Stations %>% select(name, lat,long) %>% rename(sstation = name)

Simple2 <- Simple %>% rename(estation = sstation, lat2 = lat, long2 = long)

StationPairs <- merge(Simple, Simple2, by = NULL)

PairDistances <-  StationPairs %>% mutate(distance = haversine(lat, long, lat2, long2)) %>% select(sstation, estation, distance)

RideDistances <- Trips %>% inner_join(PairDistances)
